caption.p: Oxidative stress measurements by (a) GSH enzyme activity and (b) SOD enzyme activity. (c) Representative fluorescence images showing ROS production in control and 1000 μg/ml of AG-ME. (d) Quantification of ROS production in MCF-7 cells treated with AG-ME at 250-1000 μg/ml. ∗ p < 0.05 and ∗∗ p < 0.01 vs. the control.
